#: app/Modules/Admin.php:112
msgid ""
"Some of these settings are controlled by Otomaties core. To update these "
"settings, please contact the website administrator."
msgstr ""
"Sommige van deze instellingen worden beheerd door Otomaties core. Neem "
"contact op met de websitebeheerder om deze instellingen bij te werken."

#: app/Modules/Admin.php:154
#, php-format
msgid ""
"Super page cache TTL is not set. Please configure it in the plugin settings "
"to ensure optimal caching performance. Recommendation: %s seconds."
msgstr ""
"Super page cache TTL is niet ingesteld. Configureer dit in de plug-in-"
"instellingen om optimale cacheprestaties te garanderen. Aanbeveling: %s "
"seconden."

